                      </h5>
                      <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
                        125+ caste/ethnic groups with distinct languages and
                        cultures
                      </p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <h5 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-venus-mars text-pink-600 mr-2"></i>
                        Gender Diversity
                      </h5>
                      <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
                        Increasing female participation but underrepresentation
                        in leadership
                      </p>
